    <abstract id="aspace_eabcd9b3beb5402750dca9bef84ab3ad" label="Abstract">The collection consists of photographs of members of various refugee communities in New York state, including immigrants from Vietnam, the Ukraine, Haiti, Cambodia, and elsewhere.</abstract>
